==Medals==
Many wardens went considerably beyond the call of duty and a search of medal citations in the &quot;London Gazette&quot; demonstrates this. The first ARP warden to receive the George Cross was Thomas Alderson, who won his award for actions saving civilian life in Bridlington in 1940.

